ANALYSIS OF CONSUMER PREFERENCES FOR BEER 

M. Maximovа, E. Zemlyakova 

Presents the results of a poll of consumers in Kaliningrad, whose goal was to study the demand for beer, the definition of criteria for selecting this type of beverage, the taste preferences of the respondents and their relation to the special beers, which include natural herbal supplements.






